{
  "texts": [
    "In total, researchers have applied DL techniques for eight tasks in BRM.",
    "Bug report refinementWhen a bug report is submitted, bug report refinement aims to refine the bug report and improve its quality for better understanding.",
    "For example, we can enrich the bug report with more information collected from similar bug reports or reformulate the content of the bug report.",
    "DL can be used to improve the refinement process.",
    "Zhou et al. [641] reformulated a bug report as a query representation by leveraging multi-level embeddings through CNNs with the self-attention mechanism."
  ]
}